metadata.name: F.S GIRLS -"DAINA"
metadata.description:
Name: DAINA.

She has excellent skills as a technician and is good at dealing with emergencies. She is clumsy in expressing her feelings and little dull tempered, but she is considerate and takes care of others. 

Also, if you give her a big doll as a gift, you can see her really happy face.

1. Freestyle F.S. GIRLS-1 character.

2. Buyers of the work can request for a full-body illustration commission for the character.



2500*2500Pixel 300DPI
